# Forecast: China Naval Blockade of Taiwan before 2028

[Blockade Before 2028]: China will initiate a naval blockade of Taiwan before January 1, 2028, meaning sustained interdiction of maritime traffic to major ports lasting 10+ days using PLA Navy, Coast Guard, or maritime militia. #synthesis
{credence: 0.14, reason: "final all-things-considered estimate"}


