### Historical Base Rates {isGroup: true}

[Historical Rarity]: Since 1945, approximately 3 major-power naval blockades have occurred in ~80 years (Cuba 1962, Falklands 1982, plus borderline cases), giving a ~4% annual base rate for any major power blockading a significant target. #base-rate
